		</apparel>
	</ThingDef>
	
	<ThingDef ParentName="RS13_ArmorMachineableBase">
		<defName>RS13_Clothing_RiotSuit</defName>
		<label>Riot Suit</label>
		<description>This, combined with the riot shield, will make you be the nightmare of fire extinguisher-wielding assistants everywhere. Gives complete protection to the entire body.</description>
